: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/kids-bedroom-design-060125-833-15.jpg\" alt=\"A contemporary kids bedroom in a villa in Vietnam.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/kids-bedroom-design-060125-833-15.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/kids-bedroom-design-060125-833-15-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/kids-bedroom-design-060125-833-15-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/kids-bedroom-design-060125-833-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/kids-bedroom-design-060125-833-15-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/bathroom-design-060125-833-16.jpg\" alt=\"A contemporary bathroom in a villa in Vietnam.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/bathroom-design-060125-833-16.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/bathroom-design-060125-833-16-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/bathroom-design-060125-833-16-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/bathroom-design-060125-833-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/bathroom-design-060125-833-16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eGlass blocks have been used on a curved section of the wall, allowing the natural light to pass through to the bathroom, without sacrificing privacy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1706\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-glass-blocks-balcony-060125-833-17.jpg\" alt=\"Glass blocks have been used on a curved section of the wall, allowing the natural light to pass through to the bathroom, without sacrificing privacy.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-glass-blocks-balcony-060125-833-17.jpg 1706w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-glass-blocks-balcony-060125-833-17-940x1411.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-glass-blocks-balcony-060125-833-17-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-glass-blocks-balcony-060125-833-17-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-glass-blocks-balcony-060125-833-17-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-glass-blocks-balcony-060125-833-17-1365x2048.jpg 1365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1706px) 100vw, 1706px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eSpiral stairs lead to the rooftop where a gathering space can be found.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-wall-architecture-060125-833-18.jpg\" alt=\"Spiral stairs lead to the rooftop of this villa where a gathering space can be found.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-wall-architecture-060125-833-18.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-wall-architecture-060125-833-18-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-wall-architecture-060125-833-18-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-wall-architecture-060125-833-18-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-wall-architecture-060125-833-18-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/curved-wall-architecture-060125-833-18-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/round-window-060125-831-19.jpg\" alt=\"Spiral stairs lead to the rooftop of this villa where a gathering space can be found.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/round-window-060125-831-19.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/round-window-060125-831-19-940x940.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/round-window-060125-831-19-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/round-window-060125-831-19-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/round-window-060125-831-19-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/round-window-060125-831-19-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere’s a look at the architectural drawings for the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1371\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/white-villa-lots-of-plants-indoor-swimming-pool-060124-20.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural drawings for a villa with lots of plants and an indoor swimming pool.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/white-villa-lots-of-plants-indoor-swimming-pool-060124-20.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/white-villa-lots-of-plants-indoor-swimming-pool-060124-20-940x671.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/white-